title: Ep. 778 - Special Coupons  - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The people of Gokuldham finally have received the pamphlets and they are excited for the same. Iyer wants to cancel the plan but the rest convince him not to do so.

title: Ep. 779 - All Set For The Picnic - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The residents are all set for the picnic. They even hire a traveler for the same. Jetha still hasn't reached the location and is stuck with some work.

title: Ep. 780 - A Fun - Filled Day - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha surprises the rest and they are really happy to see him. They get on different rides and have loads of fun. Iyer challenges Jetha and he loses which makes Iyer really happy.

title: Ep. 781 - The Fun Continues - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The people are still having fun in the amusement park. Meanwhile, Iyer loses his way. Bagha gives him company. Bhide teases Chachaji and Jetha. The kids have fun as well.

title: Ep. 782 - Gogi Is Missing - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: First, the residents find out that Iyer is missing. He returns and they finally leave for their house. Later, the power goes and they fix it. In this process, Gogi goes missing.

title: Ep. 783 - The Search Is Successful - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Roshan and Sodhi are worried about Gogi. The search is on. Later, they find out that Gogi was in the house itself and have laughter.

title: Ep. 784 - Kite Festival - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The residents are finally at peace. Iyer, Bhide call up Sundar for some information. The residents are busy setting up the kites. They fly kites and have fun.

title: Ep. 785 - Bhide And Madhavi's Banter - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide is teased by his wife and his daughter about the aspects. In Jetha's house as well, the banter continues between Daya and Jetha.

title: Ep. 786 - Bhide's Broken Glasses - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide has broken his glasses and there's a need to repair it. Madhavi forces him to buy a new pair of glasses. He finally agrees and goes with Popatlal. But, in his misery will he buy the new glasses?

title: Ep. 787 - Bhide Shouts At Tapu - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The kids are playing when Bhide arrives. His glasses almost slip from his hand. Later, he sees his specs broke and blames Tapu. He scolds him in front of everybody.

title: Ep. 788 - Tapu Accepts His Mistake - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide wears broken glasses. He gives notice to the person to accept their mistake. Jetha is confident that his son hasn't done anything. Has Tapu really committed the mistake?

title: Ep. 789 - The Real Culprit - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha is ready to punish his son when Sonu comes and accepts his mistake. This makes Bhide really furious. Bhide is also hurt by the fact that she is scared of him. Later, a relative of Jetha comes to their house.

title: Ep. 790 - Jetha's Trip - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha is ready to go for a trip and has asked Bagha to confirm the tickets. He is also happy as Babita will come along. But, are the tickets confirmed?

title: Ep. 801 - Jethalal In Pakistan - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everybody is concerned as Jetha is missing. They go in search of him. Meanwhile, Jetha is found strolling in Pakistan and doesn't realise it. He is finally taken to the Pakistan rangers' camp and questioned.

title: Ep. 803 - Doubts On Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha is doubted for being a informer from India. He, therefore is put behind bars where he enjoys with the others. The Pakistan police question his identity and he is left with no choice.
